  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357000/extras/69e0d251b7e34b67b19cab4efacd404a.poster.avif?t=1772093751\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357000/extras/69e0d251b7e34b67b19cab4efacd404a.webm?t=1772093751\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357000/extras/69e0d251b7e34b67b19cab4efacd404a.mp4?t=1772093751\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are the Exterminator on a crusade against the spider horde taking over the multiverse. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play solo or with friends via online co-op for up to 4 players, blast through the story campaign, and show these pests who’s boss. Or, jump into a frenetic Humans vs Spiders PvP mode for some laughs and screams. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whatever you choose, one thing is certain – it’s time to KILL IT WITH FIRE!!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357000/extras/a8e46f7e19cfe78239a368b16a8d7f8c.avif?t=1772093751\" width=1170 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357000/extras/12b872f73b449b08d15b7d0c9076e35e.poster.avif?t=1772093751\" width=1170 height=656 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357000/extras/12b872f73b449b08d15b7d0c9076e35e.webm?t=1772093751\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357000/extras/12b872f73b449b08d15b7d0c9076e35e.mp4?t=1772093751\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wage war on the eight-legged monsters with an arsenal of 45 weapons and gadgets worthy of the Exterminator. Will your team smash the pests with a newspaper, burn them to a crisp, rev up the minigun, unleash a rocket launcher, or wield a laser sword?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357000/extras/7ff015d27210aff282ba3c0207fc5c9e.avif?t=1772093751\" width=1170 height=150 /></span>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357000/extras/19fad8b051775741df6b670772078bf9.poster.avif?t=1772093751\" width=1170 height=656 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357000/extras/19fad8b051775741df6b670772078bf9.webm?t=1772093751\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357000/extras/19fad8b051775741df6b670772078bf9.mp4?t=1772093751\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on an epic spider hunt across seven distinct worlds. Exterminate the pesky arachnids in a mysterious manor, liberate a town in the Wild West, explore cyberspace, and descend into Spider Hell. Every level is a unique battle against the spiders!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357000/extras/6975991f694027638dd98b63b49dbc38.avif?t=1772093751\" width=1170 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357000/extras/0192d665e94195c3947a43c51dd76b41.poster.avif?t=1772093751\" width=1170 height=660 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357000/extras/0192d665e94195c3947a43c51dd76b41.webm?t=1772093751\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357000/extras/0192d665e94195c3947a43c51dd76b41.mp4?t=1772093751\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Brew magic potions in a bubbling cauldron. Demolish a megapolis as a kaiju-sized madman. Defend a cacti-owned saloon from waves of spiders. Win a drone race in virtual reality. There are more than 60 challenges to complete!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357000/extras/e734c20e77fd259369245410c25df211.avif?t=1772093751\" width=1170 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357000/extras/6109feb7a36c865245871c2742b45d97.poster.avif?t=1772093751\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357000/extras/6109feb7a36c865245871c2742b45d97.webm?t=1772093751\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357000/extras/6109feb7a36c865245871c2742b45d97.mp4?t=1772093751\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >‘Okay, all this spider-hunting sounds fun, but what if I want to play as a spider?’ you might ask. And yes, you can indeed play as a spider in an online 8-player PvP mode called Spider Hunt. It’s actual humans vs actual arachnids (also controlled by humans)!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >7 dimensions to save from the spider onslaught</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    60+ unique in-game challenges to complete</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    45 weapons and gadgets to unlock and craft</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    A campaign that’s fully playable solo or in 4-player co-op</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    Slapstick plot written by Miles Luna (RWBY, Red vs Blue)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    'Spider Hunt’ PvP multiplayer mode for up to 8 players</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    20+ hours of content with at least 3 loud laughs guaranteed</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    15.7 billion spiders to exterminate across the multiverse</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357000/extras/69e0d251b7e34b67b19cab4efacd404a.poster.avif?t=1772093751\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357000/extras/69e0d251b7e34b67b19cab4efacd404a.webm?t=1772093751\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357000/extras/69e0d251b7e34b67b19cab4efacd404a.mp4?t=1772093751\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are the Exterminator on a crusade against the spider horde taking over the multiverse. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play solo or with friends via online co-op for up to 4 players, blast through the story campaign, and show these pests who’s boss. Or, jump into a frenetic Humans vs Spiders PvP mode for some laughs and screams. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whatever you choose, one thing is certain – it’s time to KILL IT WITH FIRE!!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357000/extras/a8e46f7e19cfe78239a368b16a8d7f8c.avif?t=1772093751\" width=1170 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357000/extras/12b872f73b449b08d15b7d0c9076e35e.poster.avif?t=1772093751\" width=1170 height=656 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357000/extras/12b872f73b449b08d15b7d0c9076e35e.webm?t=1772093751\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357000/extras/12b872f73b4